{"tid":2270096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國大選●拜登傳奇｜從政近50年三度競逐總統寶座 人生坎坷歷喪妻女痛後再失長子","createTime":"2020-11-04T01:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T01:34:21.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"541c2e2063d02f00e8a76f5bce7b21f5117f1201","tid":2270096,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MKpyvSmITFmdD9l7qpJV0SizOL8=/720x400/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4QP5MPB2ARC2XIEWNTFVHBBSKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMKpyvSmITFmdD9l7qpJV0SizOL8%3D%2F720x400%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4QP5MPB2ARC2XIEWNTFVHBBSKA.jpg&h=17fd6b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拜登（左）在兒子博拜登的病床旁宣誓就職。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n現年77歲的拜登從政經驗豐富，年輕時曾經是美國史上最年輕參議員之一，三度參與競逐總統寶座，近年因在前總統奧巴馬任內擔任副總統而為人熟悉。他的家庭相當坎坷，前妻與女兒在一場車禍中喪生，兩名兒子亦在意外中受重傷，本來在政壇前途無限的長子，也在2015年因腦癌病逝。<br />\n拜登1942年11月生於賓夕凡尼亞州斯克蘭頓（Scranton）一個中産家庭，十幾歲時隨家人搬到特拉華州，先後就讀特拉華州大學（University of Delaware）和雪城大學（Syracuse Law School）並獲得法律學位。他在大學認識第一任妻子尼莉婭（Neilia Hunter），1966年結婚，先後誕下兒子博拜登（Beau Biden）、次子亨特（Hunter Biden）及女兒娜奧米（Naomi Biden）。<br />\n拜登在1972年以30歲之齡，成為當時美國史上第二年輕的參議員，可惜在同年12月18日，尼莉婭駕車帶三名孩子出門時發生嚴重車禍。尼莉婭與13個月大的娜奧米喪生，博及亨特亦在意外中重傷，博腿部骨折、亨特則頭骨骨折。拜登在回憶錄提到，當時有想過輕生，但他不能就此拋下博及亨特。拜登後來在兒子的病床旁宣誓就職。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201104/75TMFY62P5F6JJ3BROL62QOSFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201104%2F75TMFY62P5F6JJ3BROL62QOSFE%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3Vcynf7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=bd1533be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201104%2F75TMFY62P5F6JJ3BROL62QOSFE%2F&h=55d2fde7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201104/75TMFY62P5F6JJ3BROL62QOSFE/</a>"},{"pid":"d8869fcf5f54af9dfbff32e42ee508f7c87be450","tid":2270096,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:23:38.000Z","msg":"變態佬會唔會想用交通意外殺妻， 好似中大果位前教授咁"},{"pid":"69a1b6bffd3f8aeb501bdb937f1479fdc0eaff2e","tid":2270096,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbd3d957f4900aacca572e2a9899361a9b51e13","tid":2270096,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:24:52.000Z","msg":"47年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c99a1e3a9dda633e5f80aa5cc63e6435b8cc15","tid":2270096,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T01:34:21.000Z","msg":"如果佢贏，會唔會激動到爆血管死佐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}